AutoCensor vNext

This repository contains source code only. Model weights, private datasets,
personal paths, account links, API keys, telemetry, and cloud-upload code are
not included.

No fonts are bundled. Korean and English UI text is stored as UTF-8 and rendered
with operating-system font fallbacks.

Runtime dependencies are installed separately and are not relicensed by this
project. Review dependency licenses before shipping a bundled runtime.
